title: Border Incident (1949 film noir)
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0041198/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0041198/</a>

Docu-noir directed by Anthony Mann and photographed by John Alton, a pair who did many of the best noirs. In this movie, You have to get past the stentorian pro-government bullshit, but underneath that is a wonderful, very brutal police-procedure noir on the theme of illegal immigration. 


Stars Ricardo Montalban.
